    - language: 0
      text: A weak magic attack.
    - language: 1
      text: "M\u1ED9t \u0111\xF2n t\u1EA5n c\xF4ng ph\xE9p thu\u1EADt y\u1EBFu."
  - id: card_0004_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Standard magic attack.
    - language: 1
      text: "\u0110\xF2n t\u1EA5n c\xF4ng ma thu\u1EADt ti\xEAu chu\u1EA9n."
  - id: card_0005_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Recover 40 Stamina and gain 30% Action Gauge.
    - language: 1
      text: "H\u1ED3i ph\u1EE5c 40 \u0111i\u1EC3m th\u1EC3 l\u1EF1c v\xE0 t\u0103ng
        30% thanh h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng."
  - id: card_0006_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Recover 20 Stamina and Heal 5% HP.
    - language: 1
      text: "H\u1ED3i ph\u1EE5c 20 \u0111i\u1EC3m th\u1EC3 l\u1EF1c v\xE0 t\u0103ng
        5% m\xE1u."
  - id: card_0007_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Apply 1 Vulnerable effect to enemy
    - language: 1
      text: "\xC1p d\u1EE5ng 1 hi\u1EC7u \u1EE9ng \u0110i\u1EC3m y\u1EBFu cho k\u1EBB
        \u0111\u1ECBch"
  - id: card_0008_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Inflict 2 Power Down.
    - language: 1
      text: "G\xE2y 2 hi\u1EC7u \u1EE9ng Gi\u1EA3m s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh"
